MPa and total elongation of 51%. Increasing the aging\ntemperature and time, k-carbides start to form intergranularly, lose their\ncoherency with the matrix and severely compromise the hardness and strength.\nThe shearing of the carbides during deformation is also studied.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 30 Apr 2023 13:42:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 May 2023 07:07:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-04"}
